After much attempts , I finally made my own successful cup of Dalgona Milo ! 😋⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Ingredients used : ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
1) Ice and Milk as base ⁣⁣
2) 1 can of chilled all Purpose Cream ⁣⁣
3) 1 packet of instant Milo powder , using Milo Gao Siew Dai as it’s less sweet ⁣⁣
4) 2 tablespoon of sugar ⁣⁣
5) Some digestive biscuit crumbs as topping ⁣⁣
Whisk item 2 to 4 together . It’s really so much easier after using a electric whisker , thanks @rydenlee for getting it ! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Topped with some digestive biscuit crumbs and this ice cold Dalgona Milo is good to go ! ⁣⁣I’m so glad that I learn and try out this latest trend during this circuit breaker period . Not gonna waste this time ! Probably I will do up more desserts posts to share soon ! Stay tuned , stay home , stay safe ! ⁣⁣
